{"word":"G4723 - στείρος - steíros - sti'-ros - Barren","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στείρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">steíros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sti'-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Barren</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மலடியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"hard, stiff; of men and animals, barren: of a woman who does not conceive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A contraction from <a href=\"#/G4731 - στερεός - stereós - ster-eh-os'/4731\">G4731</a> (as <i>stiff</i> and <i>unnatural</i>); &ldquo;sterile&rdquo;: - barren.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}